---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Project Output">
    <section class="space-y-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Rand Water Project
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Project Output
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                New parts for water meters in pipeline infrastructure that reduce theft incentives,
                improve installation speed, and remain fully compliant.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Output Summary</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-7">
                The project delivers redesigned water meter components made from lower-value materials.
                The goal is to make meters less attractive to steal while staying compatible with existing
                pipelines and meeting legal and construction standards.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Lower Theft Value</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Less valuable to be stolen, reducing vandalism and loss of equipment.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Easy Installation</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Relatively easy to install when compared to traditional metal parts.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Pipeline Compatibility</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Fully compatible with existing pipeline infrastructure.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Standards and Compliance</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Adheres to construction standards and legal requirements.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:col-span-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Business Value</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Profitable for the company to implement through reduced losses and sustainable maintenance.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>